Package org.neo4j.io.pagecache.tracing

Interface EvictionRunEvent

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, AutoCloseablePageCacheTracerEvent, EvictionEventOpportunity
    public interface EvictionRunEvent
extends AutoCloseablePageCacheTracerEvent, EvictionEventOpportunity
    An eviction run is started when the page cache has determined that it needs to evict a batch of pages. The dedicated eviction thread is mostly sleeping when it is not performing an eviction run.
